value:
Ah... I can feel your mortal gaze
pass over me, dripping with desire.
How repulsive.

I drank of the dream nectar, and was
given a new life as a dökkálfr—a life
shaped by Lady Freyja's love.

People are happier indulging in their
fantasies than wading through this
harsh reality... Don't you agree?

I want to be loved...needed...
Isn't that what everyone dreams of?

Throughout this castle, wretched
mortals engage in questionable acts...
Utterly deplorable.

I am Plumeria, and I was sent here
by $Nf's love...

A dream of love overflowing,
a love never ending...

The grand existence of a dökkálfr
is above that of a vulgar mortal.

Hmm... And just how are you
planning to use this?

I am Plumeria, the lewd dream,
a noble dökkálfr of Dökkálfheimr.$k$pNow that you've summoned me...
what are you planning to do?

Before...I was never loved. And no
one accepted my love. And then my
mortal life ended.$k$pI wanted to feel loved...
I needed to be needed...$k$pThe love my mother had for men...
that obscene love between mortals
is something that I always detested.$k$pYet...even now, deep down, I still
want only to be loved.$k$pEven if only for a moment.
Even if it's all a lie...$k$pWill you...love me?
Yes, I am Plumeria of the dökkálfar, and I have seen your secret dreams...the ones no one else ever sees...
...Humans. You cannot help but be vulgar, can you?
The depravity of human desire seems to know no bounds... Your fantasies, beyond filthy.
You are but one of innumerable wretched humans. And yet, here I am...
